  <description>
    <p>
      ExpressLRS-Configurator is a cross platform configuration tool for the ExpressLRS firmware.
      Allowing you to configure your ExpressLRS radio module and bind it to your transmitter. Or just keep them up to date.
    </p>
  </description>
